<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-10">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Security & IT Readiness</h1>

  <p class="mb-4">
    <%= link_to 'replicate.info', root_path, class: "text-blue-600 font-semibold" %> is email-based by design. No dashboards, no logins, no integrations. The architecture minimizes risk and follows modern security practices without unnecessary complexity.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-6">
    For a DPA, security docs, or procurement review, contact
    <%= mail_to 'support@replicate.info', 'support@replicate.info', class: "text-blue-600 font-medium hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition" %>.
  </p>

  <div class="space-y-10 text-sm">

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-base">Architecture & Data</h2>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">Hosted on Heroku (AWS)</h3>
      <p>All infrastructure runs in isolated worker dynos with encrypted storage and enforced HTTPS.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">Data encrypted in transit and at rest</h3>
      <p>All data is encrypted at rest using AES-256, managed by Heroku's infrastructure.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">No customer data stored</h3>
      <p>We persist your team's email addresses and conversation history (for personalized coaching insights).</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-base">Access & Delivery</h2>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">No user accounts or logins</h3>
      <p>Coaching is delivered by email. No sessions, passwords, or user-managed devices.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">No integrations required</h3>
      <p>We do not connect to GitHub, Jira, Slack, SMTP servers, or any other internal tool.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">You own your data</h3>
      <p>Content can be exported or permanently deleted on request. Nothing is used for AI training. We can export your team's coaching history on request for internal auditing or review.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">Planned shutdowns</h3>
      <p>In the case of a planned end-of-service, customers would receive advance notice and a downloadable archive of recent coaching history, prompts, and full source code. Support would remain available through the shutdown window.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">SCIM not yet available</h3>
      <p>Account owners can manage employee access by emailing <a href="mailto:support@replicate.info" class="text-blue-600 font-medium hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition">support@replicate.info</a></p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-base">Compliance & Documentation</h2>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">DPA available on request</h3>
      <p>While replicate.info does not process customer-submitted data, a standard agreement is available for internal review.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">SOC 2 not yet available</h3>
      <p>Documentation is available for teams evaluating vendor readiness.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-1 text-base">Subprocessors</h2>

      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm mt-4 space-y-1">
        <li>Heroku (AWS) — Infrastructure and encrypted storage</li>
        <li>OpenAI — Language generation. Data is sent for one-time processing only. Nothing is stored or retained.</li>
        <li>Postmark — Transactional email delivery (no click/open tracking)</li>
        <li>Stripe — Payment processing</li>
        <li>Google Analytics — Measuring basic marketing website traffic</li>
      </ul>

    </div>

  </div>

  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-6">
    <%= link_to 'Terms of Service', '/terms', class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline" %> &nbsp;&nbsp;•&nbsp;&nbsp;
    <%= link_to 'Privacy Policy', '/privacy', class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline" %>
  </p>
</div>